      <title>风电发电量下降导致德国电力供应紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/germany-expecting-tight-power-conditions-as-wind-output-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[风力发电量低和天气寒冷导致德国电力系统利润率今年冬季降至最低，价格可能上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/germany-expecting-tight-power-conditions-as-wind-output-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
